For storing the values in c we are using the "scanf" keyword.
Here "&" plays an very important role in the time of storing the values in c.
for storing the integers values we are using this method 
Ex:printf("%d",&variablename);
for storing the string value
Ex:printf("%s",& variablename);

for storing the characters values
Ex:printf("%c",& variabkename);

for storing the floating values
Ex: printf("%f",& varaiblename);
